* GeoIP module

  Check ChunZhen IP database from web interface
    Very Simple: query url then strip result.
  Check GeoIP from locale installed GeoIP database
    Need addational GeoIP installation
    API level coding.

  CommandLine sample: <Sombody> ~geoip xx.xx[.xx][.xx]
    [.xx][.xx] default to .0.1
    [.xx] default to .1

  Result sample: <BadGirl> xx.xx.xx.xx: location